    "title": "Principal Frontend Developer at Salesforce India Ventures Solutions",
    "description": "We at Salesforce India Ventures Solutions are looking for an experienced Frontend Developer based out of Kolkata. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Salesforce India Ventures Solutions:\nSalesforce India Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Python\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Referral bonus program\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kolkata, West Bengal, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Salesforce India Ventures Solutions!",
